<HEADLINE> Chinese Military Leader Meets Russian Defense Secretary </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, January 22 (Xinhua) -- Chi Haotian, vice-chairman of
China's Central Military Commission, met with Andrei Kokoshin,
chief military inspector and secretary of Russia's Defense
Council, here today.
</P>
<P>
Chi welcomed Kokoshin to China, and said he was glad to see the
friendship and cooperative ties between China and its neighbor
Russia, and between their armies, constantly advance over the
years.
</P>
<P>
The many meetings of President Jiang Zemin and President Boris
Yeltsin indicate that China and Russia are good neighbors, good
friends and good partners, Chi said, adding that the meetings also
reflect the maturing strategic cooperative partnership between the
two nations.
</P>
<P>
