that he believed the visit would raise the friendship and
cooperation between the two armies to a new level.
</P>
<P>
Kokoshin said that Yeltsin also is paying attention to his
tour, which the Russian president believes will strengthen ties
between the two armies.
</P>
<P>
Also attending the meeting was Wu Quanxu, deputy chief of the
general staff of the Chinese People's Liberation Army. 
</P>
