is facing an acute financial crisis.
</P>
<P>
During a briefing at the PIA headquarters in Karachi,
Pakistan's biggest city, Sharif said a committee has been set up
to work out a new aviation policy so as to make the PIA an
excellent airline as it was in the 1960s, according to the
