<TEXT>
<P>
GUANGZHOU, January 22 (Xinhua) -- The Guangdong Provincial Bone
Marrow Bank opened today in Guangzhou, capital of south China's
Province.
</P>
<P>
More than 100 donors from all walks of life showed up on
opening day.
</P>
<P>
The bank was pioneered by the People's Hospital of
Guangdong. Up to date, more than 1,000 residents of the province
have expressed a willingness to donate bone marrow to leukemia
victims.
</P>
<P>
