on the Chinese Communists and people to learn from the selfless
internationalist.
</P>
<P>
Deng Xiaoping and President Jiang Zemin wrote inscriptions,
urging people to carry out Dr. Bethune's spirit.
</P>
<P>
At today's ceremony, 13 teams of Chinese Young Pioneers from
across the country stood in front of his tomb, pledging to follow
his example. 
