<TEXT>
<P>
KUALA LUMPUR, January 22 (Xinhua) -- The third APEC (Asia
Pacific Economic Cooperation) International Trade Fair '98 will be
held in Malaysia from November 13 to 16, 1998, it was announced
here Thursday.
</P>
<P>
