Council of Baltic Sea States as an organization that discusses
projects for practical economic cooperation."
</P>
<P>
The three Baltic states on January 16 signed with the United
States a partnership Charter, which disturbed Moscow so much.
Russia holds that it indicates the beginning of preparations for
the next stage of NATO's eastward expansion, since the three
Baltic states refuse to accept the security guarantees proposal by
the Russian president. 
