<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, January 21 (Xinhua) -- A Catholic man in his min-50s
was shot dead by gunmen this afternoon as he sat in his car in a
loyalist area of Belfast, police said.
</P>
<P>
An eyewitness said he heard five shots and ran out to find the
man slumped in the car. The victim, shot in the chest and neck,
died in an ambulance.
